Utterance.UttText: In Bed 2, we have Dylan Young, 41 yrs old under Dr Fleming, came in with headaches, vision and speech problems.
He is a new admission today.
He needs assistance when walking to the toilet because he cant see properly and we cannot seem to understand what he is saying so he really need a lot of time before you can understand what he wants.
Sometimes he does some sign languages or sometimes he just write down what he wants.
He is on general diet and He's obs are all normal.
He is for daily bloods, and he is on regular analgesia for pain.
